WEBVTT

00:14.960 --> 00:18.300
This withered tree has not bloomed
or grown leaves for decades.

00:18.710 --> 00:20.170
Why sweep every day

00:20.440 --> 00:23.100
when there is nothing to clean up?

00:24.280 --> 00:25.319
Master says

00:25.320 --> 00:26.850
sweeping is part of our cultivation.

00:26.960 --> 00:28.119
Regardless of fallen leaves,

00:28.120 --> 00:29.850
it must be swept daily.

00:31.000 --> 00:32.140
How stubborn.

00:32.830 --> 00:34.359
The Abbot was referring

00:34.360 --> 00:35.540
to your heart,

00:35.640 --> 00:37.370
not just this small patch of ground.

00:37.710 --> 00:38.850
It's raining.

00:39.110 --> 00:40.349
Come sit with me for a while.

00:40.350 --> 00:41.940
Have some tea to kill time.

00:50.560 --> 00:52.090
The old tree has blossomed!

00:52.710 --> 00:53.850
Look!

01:07.920 --> 01:10.010
(You were born emotionally detached)

01:10.070 --> 01:11.580
(and indifferent since childhood.)

01:11.950 --> 01:13.610
(Like this withered tree.)

01:13.790 --> 01:15.250
(Although there's life,)

01:15.310 --> 01:16.999
(it bears no flowers or leaves.)

01:17.000 --> 01:19.300
This withered tree neither blooms

01:19.310 --> 01:20.530
nor grows leaves.

01:20.950 --> 01:22.650
Its dark, lifeless appearance

01:23.350 --> 01:25.340
doesn't fit with the elegance
of this courtyard.

01:26.150 --> 01:28.140
Why not have someone dig it up
and toss it out?

01:30.590 --> 01:34.370
Every living thing
has its purpose for existing.

01:34.590 --> 01:37.010
One day, when you've grown

01:37.120 --> 01:39.090
and experienced the world,

01:39.430 --> 01:43.890
you'll understand
that even a withered tree can revive.

01:46.040 --> 01:48.340
If I can understand when I'm older,

01:49.290 --> 01:52.650
why did my father send me here, then?

01:54.560 --> 01:57.500
Everyone has their own path in life.

01:57.510 --> 02:01.479
Being emotionally detached
may be a burden in the world.

02:01.480 --> 02:04.700
But in the Buddhist realm,
it can be a blessing.

02:05.000 --> 02:06.780
You are fated to walk this path,

02:06.840 --> 02:10.610
so your Dharma name will be Yuantong.

03:42.780 --> 03:46.939
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:46.940 --> 03:50.200
=Episode 18=

03:53.730 --> 03:55.150
Come and take a look, sir.

03:58.400 --> 03:59.749
(Now, this is weird.)

03:59.750 --> 04:01.330
(He's even sending me back home.)

04:01.550 --> 04:03.890
(The fierce soldier has turned
into someone compassionate.)

04:03.910 --> 04:05.399
(What is he up to?)

04:05.400 --> 04:06.620
Come and take a look.

04:17.480 --> 04:18.389
(Oh my.)

04:18.390 --> 04:20.740
(I once accused the Dou Family
of having ulterior motives.)

04:20.830 --> 04:22.860
(Now, I'm the one with a motive.)

04:24.430 --> 04:26.420
(How can I change this impression?)

04:26.980 --> 04:30.120
(Dou's Residence)

04:35.720 --> 04:38.250
Thank you for saving me earlier,
Your Lordship.

04:38.360 --> 04:41.460
You even took time escorting me back.

04:41.920 --> 04:44.170
I acted rashly
during the Dragon Boat Festival.

04:44.530 --> 04:45.799
Please take this as my apology.

04:45.800 --> 04:47.860
I hope you can forgive me, Official Dou.

04:49.360 --> 04:50.500
See you.

04:52.610 --> 04:54.860
You're not here to propose, are you?

04:57.240 --> 04:58.380
No, I'm not.

04:58.540 --> 05:01.239
I was on duty today

05:01.240 --> 05:02.420
and just happened to pass by.

05:02.720 --> 05:05.159
But the incident with your horse
wasn't purely coincidental.

05:05.160 --> 05:06.999
Firecrackers don't go off on their own.

05:07.000 --> 05:08.460
My man is investigating.

05:08.720 --> 05:11.730
I hear you've offended some
by rejecting marriage proposals

05:12.120 --> 05:13.370
for your fourth daughter.

05:15.190 --> 05:17.740
A man without faults
can still be envied for his treasures.

05:17.750 --> 05:19.580
When you possess
something precious like jade,

05:19.590 --> 05:22.350
giving it up too easily
as "The Spring and Autumn Annals" says

05:22.360 --> 05:24.050
only leads to it
being taken for granted.

05:24.120 --> 05:26.860
Ms. Longevity is far more valuable
than a piece of priceless jade.

05:27.010 --> 05:28.639
I'd sooner resign from my post

05:28.640 --> 05:30.730
than allow her
to be with those scoundrels.

05:31.240 --> 05:33.020
(Her father might seem soft by nature.)

05:33.030 --> 05:35.400
(When it comes to major issues,
he does have some backbone.)

05:36.420 --> 05:39.350
Your Lordship, do you enjoy reading
"The Spring and Autumn Annals" as well?

05:40.210 --> 05:41.730
I only browse through it occasionally.

05:41.740 --> 05:43.799
The lessons
in "The Spring and Autumn Annals" reveal

05:43.800 --> 05:45.230
new insights each time you read it.

05:45.680 --> 05:46.860
When time allows,

05:47.800 --> 05:49.020
we must discuss it further.

05:49.390 --> 05:50.530
Certainly.

05:50.720 --> 05:51.860
Don't let me keep you.

05:57.160 --> 05:59.410
Lu Ming, buy me a copy
of "The Spring and Autumn Annals."

05:59.420 --> 06:01.690
Make sure it's the latest edition
with the imperial annotations.

06:01.700 --> 06:03.690
I thought Your Lordship had
a photographic memory.

06:03.750 --> 06:06.069
You read it once and sent it
to the orphanage afterward.

06:06.070 --> 06:07.930
Did I ever say I bought it to read?

06:08.190 --> 06:09.540
It's for display.

06:11.200 --> 06:13.189
You're not reading
"The Spring and Autumn Annals,"

06:13.190 --> 06:14.570
but romance.

06:15.910 --> 06:18.429
Your Lordship, we've caught the person
who startled the horse.

06:18.430 --> 06:19.860
It was Hai Changbo's servant.

06:20.040 --> 06:21.589
He refused to say anything.

06:21.590 --> 06:22.810
Does he even need to?

06:22.850 --> 06:24.159
It's obvious he was upset

06:24.160 --> 06:25.660
because his proposal was rejected.

06:25.830 --> 06:28.490
But this firecracker is larger
than normal.

06:28.630 --> 06:31.100
It's already against regulation.

06:31.310 --> 06:32.919
Someone's likely hiding gunpowder.

06:32.920 --> 06:34.130
Should we investigate?

06:38.280 --> 06:39.119
Let's do it.

06:39.120 --> 06:41.050
It's also a good chance
to deal with Hai Changbo.

06:42.780 --> 06:44.680
(Twilight in Spring)

06:48.100 --> 06:49.100
(Imperial Gift)

06:49.110 --> 06:51.390
If anyone pressures you
to discuss marriage in the future,

06:51.400 --> 06:52.300
just show them this.

06:52.600 --> 06:53.930
You have the right to choose

06:54.190 --> 06:55.780
and to refuse.

06:56.630 --> 06:58.930
Even if it's your father or your uncle,

06:59.190 --> 07:01.050
no one can force you anymore.

07:01.680 --> 07:04.170
He could have asked
His Majesty to grant him the marriage.

07:04.680 --> 07:06.900
But instead, he requested His Majesty

07:06.920 --> 07:08.610
to allow you to marry freely.

07:09.630 --> 07:12.660
It shows he genuinely wants
the best for you.

07:13.000 --> 07:14.660
If you agree to marry me,

07:15.160 --> 07:17.509
hang a red tassel on this magnolia tree

07:17.510 --> 07:18.930
in five days.

07:19.360 --> 07:20.810
I can see it from afar.

07:21.240 --> 07:22.380
If you don't,

07:23.160 --> 07:24.370
hang a white one,

07:26.000 --> 07:28.980
and I'll never bother you again.

07:34.510 --> 07:35.650
Little Zhuang Zhou,

07:37.390 --> 07:38.570
Ji Jianming?

07:38.700 --> 07:39.930
What are you doing here?

07:40.160 --> 07:41.419
What did I tell you?

07:41.420 --> 07:42.579
After all that,

07:42.580 --> 07:44.080
they still ended up getting married.

07:44.240 --> 07:45.539
Now, you're hiding in Zhending.

07:45.540 --> 07:47.280
Do you think
you can stay hidden forever?

07:48.580 --> 07:50.939
This situation could blow up
or be resolved quietly.

07:50.940 --> 07:52.499
If a clever person doesn't step in,

07:52.500 --> 07:54.840
it could cause a lot of trouble
for the Dou Family.

07:55.380 --> 07:56.920
Do you want to hear my solution?

07:57.380 --> 07:59.360
I'm not interested in any tricks
that harm others

07:59.380 --> 08:00.460
for personal gain.

08:00.480 --> 08:02.059
It's not about personal gain this time.

08:02.060 --> 08:03.680
It's me sacrificing for others.

08:04.620 --> 08:06.880
Let's take this to the next level
and get married.

08:09.540 --> 08:11.440
Gosh, Ji Jianming!

08:11.660 --> 08:14.139
You and I share
a deep and pure friendship.

08:14.140 --> 08:16.480
I don't want to take anything
to the next level with you.

08:17.260 --> 08:18.680
You said it,

08:18.700 --> 08:20.519
you and I share a deep
and pure friendship.

08:20.520 --> 08:22.139
From now on, don't say anything nonsense

08:22.140 --> 08:23.840
like going separate ways again.

08:25.900 --> 08:27.050
Childish.

08:38.140 --> 08:39.280
It's repaired?

08:39.420 --> 08:41.179
It isn't easy
to repair this foreign item.

08:41.180 --> 08:43.190
It's going to cost more
than just buying a new one.

08:43.200 --> 08:45.019
Yeah, it cost three months of my salary.

08:45.020 --> 08:47.040
A little keepsake
to mark our reconciliation.

08:50.220 --> 08:51.600
Don't break it again.

08:52.340 --> 08:53.480
Also,

08:53.540 --> 08:55.629
your father said not to go back
if anything happens.

08:55.630 --> 08:56.920
He'll handle it all.

08:59.620 --> 09:02.629
But no matter what we choose now,

09:02.630 --> 09:04.040
someone is bound to be upset.

09:05.260 --> 09:07.360
If Father doesn't choose a side,

09:07.500 --> 09:09.299
it's going to offend the imperial family

09:09.300 --> 09:10.640
and upset the emperor.

09:11.580 --> 09:13.240
My father is a scholar at heart,

09:14.060 --> 09:15.440
he doesn't understand how to adapt.

09:15.860 --> 09:17.240
He won't be able to handle it.

09:17.820 --> 09:20.840
But I can't let this matter fall
into Fifth Uncle's hands.

09:21.700 --> 09:23.200
Are you worried that Fifth Master Dou

09:23.230 --> 09:24.499
might use your marriage

09:24.500 --> 09:25.579
to drag the Dou Family

09:25.580 --> 09:27.840
into the power struggle over the throne?

09:30.730 --> 09:32.240
Politics in officialdom are dangerous.

09:32.360 --> 09:34.480
Many have lost their lives

09:35.080 --> 09:36.480
in pursuit of fame and power.

09:36.780 --> 09:38.680
I only want a peaceful, joyful,

09:39.260 --> 09:40.920
free, and stable life.

09:57.300 --> 09:58.680
Teach me to read the stars.

10:02.260 --> 10:05.230
You have the fate to understand the causes
of the universe.

10:05.240 --> 10:06.680
Why do you need to look at the stars?

10:06.690 --> 10:08.760
But the road ahead is dark,

10:08.940 --> 10:10.520
and I can't see anything.

10:11.900 --> 10:14.120
Why cling to the mundane world?

10:14.260 --> 10:16.120
Exploring the world, sailing the seas,

10:16.140 --> 10:17.320
how delightful it is.

10:20.660 --> 10:24.440
Do you remember anything
from your past life?

10:26.310 --> 10:27.619
Who could possibly remember that?

10:27.620 --> 10:30.259
When I read the stars,
I can only see the present.

10:30.260 --> 10:31.880
I don't claim to know everything.

10:34.940 --> 10:37.840
Is everything in life destined?

10:39.140 --> 10:41.539
Will what's meant to happen

10:41.540 --> 10:43.440
will happen?

10:45.660 --> 10:47.160
Have you heard of planetary movements?

10:47.500 --> 10:49.499
As the stars shift, so do people.

10:49.500 --> 10:51.019
If everything were truly fated,

10:51.020 --> 10:52.859
why would you be worrying here?

10:52.860 --> 10:54.579
It's because life is full of uncertainty

10:54.580 --> 10:56.000
that it's so fascinating.

11:05.980 --> 11:08.520
(Zhaowen Bookstore)

11:10.580 --> 11:12.280
Young Lady, you're back.

11:15.020 --> 11:16.680
What has Song Mo been up to lately?

11:16.900 --> 11:21.520
Song Mo is just doing his usual duties.

11:22.020 --> 11:23.633
By the way, Hai Changbo

11:23.634 --> 11:26.320
is suspected of privately making
gunpowder and firecrackers.

11:26.780 --> 11:29.120
Song Mo is investigating the case.

11:29.260 --> 11:30.440
Well, well.

11:30.860 --> 11:33.800
He's still working in the court
and investigating cases?

11:34.500 --> 11:35.779
At a time like this,

11:35.780 --> 11:37.800
he still have the mind
to investigate cases?

11:38.500 --> 11:39.859
Is there anything wrong?

11:39.860 --> 11:41.160
Nothing is wrong.

11:41.380 --> 11:42.739
He does his job,

11:42.740 --> 11:44.000
and I'll do mine.

11:45.380 --> 11:46.520
Manager Zhao,

11:47.380 --> 11:49.440
show me the latest gold-spotted paper.

11:50.500 --> 11:52.459
His Lordship is part
of the Imperial Guard.

11:52.460 --> 11:55.120
What's wrong with him going to court?

11:58.220 --> 11:59.659
Higher!

11:59.660 --> 12:01.179
A little higher!

12:01.180 --> 12:02.959
- Why is it white?
- Higher!

12:02.960 --> 12:04.939
- Fifth Master sent you to the manor,
- Come on, a little higher!

12:04.940 --> 12:06.899
- and now you sneak back home.
- I said, higher.

12:06.900 --> 12:08.659
What if someone notices?

12:08.660 --> 12:10.059
Higher.

12:10.060 --> 12:11.640
- Let's go back, Young Lady.
- Higher.

12:11.660 --> 12:12.549
Su Xin,

12:12.550 --> 12:14.800
- take down that white kite.
- A little higher.

12:15.220 --> 12:16.360
Yes, Young Lady.

12:17.220 --> 12:18.360
I'll do it.

12:19.020 --> 12:20.720
How did you get into this courtyard?

12:20.980 --> 12:23.939
The gatekeeper let us in
to pick up the kite.

12:23.940 --> 12:25.259
Stop playing under this tree.

12:25.260 --> 12:26.400
Understand?

12:26.460 --> 12:27.600
Come on, let's go.

12:35.740 --> 12:36.819
Su Xin,

12:36.820 --> 12:38.800
take down that white tail too.

12:38.820 --> 12:39.960
- Hurry.
- Yes, Young Lady.

12:45.100 --> 12:46.980
The firecracker factory
on the city's outskirts

12:46.990 --> 12:48.459
is indeed connected to Hai Changbo.

12:48.460 --> 12:51.699
It turns out Hai Changbo
has been colluding with people

12:51.700 --> 12:53.160
from the eastern Shenji Camp.

12:53.660 --> 12:55.760
Hai Changbo is someone close
to Lord Qing.

12:55.820 --> 12:58.160
So this batch of gunpowder
is linked to Lord Qing as well.

12:58.820 --> 13:00.000
Does that mean Lord Qing

13:00.620 --> 13:02.499
is involved with the Shenji Camp too?

13:02.500 --> 13:03.970
If that's the case, then Hai Changbo

13:03.980 --> 13:06.880
did that not only
for the proposal rejection.

13:08.580 --> 13:09.720
Your Lordship!

13:11.460 --> 13:13.939
Your Lordship, I've discovered
someone has been tailing me.

13:13.940 --> 13:15.579
I was worried it was Hai Changbo's men.

13:15.580 --> 13:17.730
So I captured the person
and interrogated him harshly.

13:17.740 --> 13:18.880
Then...

13:19.620 --> 13:21.200
What happened next? Speak quickly.

13:22.380 --> 13:23.680
He confessed.

13:23.940 --> 13:25.540
He said

13:26.100 --> 13:27.560
he worked for Chen Qushui.

13:28.620 --> 13:31.160
Chen Qushui's people
were tailing His Lordship?

13:32.220 --> 13:33.680
But Chen Qushui

13:33.820 --> 13:36.040
and Hai Changbo
have no connection at all.

13:36.540 --> 13:38.200
If he's Chen Qushui's man,

13:39.260 --> 13:40.960
then he's also Dou Zhao's people.

13:43.260 --> 13:46.000
Dou Zhao actually sent someone
to follow me?

13:48.300 --> 13:49.579
Yet, you beat him up?

13:49.580 --> 13:51.890
How else would I have known
he was working for Chen Qushui?

13:51.900 --> 13:53.150
But don't worry, Your Lordship.

13:53.160 --> 13:55.379
This guy is weak.

13:55.380 --> 13:56.819
He confessed pretty quickly.

13:56.820 --> 14:01.880
I didn't go too hard on him.

14:05.300 --> 14:07.040
What should I do now?

14:08.860 --> 14:10.480
I couldn't take the beating.

14:10.500 --> 14:11.760
So I gave in.

14:11.820 --> 14:14.219
Later, Lord Song loosened
my bonds himself.

14:14.220 --> 14:16.619
Then he gave me a gold ingot

14:16.620 --> 14:18.080
and let me go.

14:18.660 --> 14:20.979
Did His Lordship say anything?

14:20.980 --> 14:22.160
His Lordship asked me

14:22.460 --> 14:25.160
to send his regards to you.

14:27.220 --> 14:29.640
I've never seen
so much money in my life.

14:29.760 --> 14:31.099
So I didn't dare act recklessly.

14:31.100 --> 14:34.000
So I brought
the gold ingot back to you.

14:34.100 --> 14:35.299
It must have been hard on you.

14:35.300 --> 14:37.899
Consider this gold as your medicine fee.

14:37.900 --> 14:39.120
Take it.

14:42.260 --> 14:44.240
Thank you, Fourth Young Lady!

14:49.100 --> 14:50.240
Fourth Young Lady,

14:50.260 --> 14:52.040
it's my fault
for choosing the wrong person.

14:52.380 --> 14:55.240
Please punish me.

14:55.700 --> 14:58.099
I asked you
to send someone to follow him.

14:58.100 --> 14:59.560
It's not your fault.

15:01.540 --> 15:04.560
I just feel embarrassed
about this whole situation.

15:05.940 --> 15:07.080
Young Lady,

15:08.220 --> 15:10.680
why don't you have some snacks
and rest for a while?

15:19.420 --> 15:20.300
What happened?

15:20.320 --> 15:23.179
It seems there was an explosion
at a firecracker factory in the suburbs.

15:23.180 --> 15:25.840
I don't know if Lord Song is there.

15:29.050 --> 15:30.240
Fetch the water!

15:31.700 --> 15:32.940
Put out the fire!

15:36.380 --> 15:37.720
- Fetch more water!
- Quickly!

15:38.420 --> 15:39.419
Over here!

15:39.420 --> 15:40.539
Why is there an explosion?

15:40.540 --> 15:42.120
Whose firecracker factory is it?

15:46.060 --> 15:47.200
Song Mo!

15:51.780 --> 15:52.920
Song Mo!

15:52.940 --> 15:54.440
Hurry! Fetch more water!

15:54.500 --> 15:55.720
Keep the water coming!

15:56.380 --> 15:57.800
- Song Mo!
- Fourth Young Lady!

15:59.300 --> 16:00.739
Fourth Young Lady, why are you here?

16:00.740 --> 16:01.880
Where is His Lordship?

16:02.100 --> 16:03.240
I couldn't find him.

16:03.940 --> 16:05.080
What should we do now?

16:05.140 --> 16:06.280
Song Mo!

16:07.520 --> 16:08.499
Did you see His Lordship?

16:08.500 --> 16:09.579
His Lordship is inside.

16:09.580 --> 16:10.960
He hasn't come out yet.

16:11.160 --> 16:12.499
- Song Mo!
- Fourth Young Lady!

16:12.500 --> 16:13.640
Young Lady!

16:14.260 --> 16:15.400
Song Mo!

16:32.910 --> 16:34.419
Fu! Fu!

16:34.420 --> 16:36.019
I found it. It's all right now.

16:36.020 --> 16:37.430
- Thank you, sir.
- Thank you, sir.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.520
Thank you, sir.

16:38.540 --> 16:39.800
Come on, let's go.

16:39.980 --> 16:41.280
It's very dangerous here.

16:41.660 --> 16:42.800
Why are you here?

16:47.950 --> 16:49.090
Come with me.

16:58.460 --> 16:59.840
Is there anything important?

17:03.230 --> 17:05.400
I grew up in the manor

17:06.260 --> 17:09.320
and surrounded myself
with advisors and guards.

17:10.300 --> 17:11.680
My only thought

17:11.780 --> 17:13.840
was to avoid harm

17:14.640 --> 17:16.880
and live according to my own will.

17:18.340 --> 17:19.810
But never considering

17:21.380 --> 17:23.240
what I truly wanted.

17:24.220 --> 17:25.880
Until just now,

17:27.180 --> 17:28.480
then I realized.

17:32.660 --> 17:33.800
Song Mo,

17:36.080 --> 17:37.380
I like you.

17:38.670 --> 17:40.379
Actually, I've noticed

17:40.380 --> 17:42.560
I had some feelings for a long time.

17:43.500 --> 17:44.459
But I didn't dare

17:44.460 --> 17:46.480
to face a future I couldn't control.

17:46.930 --> 17:48.360
Now,

17:48.620 --> 17:50.160
I'm even more afraid of losing you.

17:57.420 --> 17:58.560
I know

17:59.020 --> 18:00.200
you have to stand tall

18:00.580 --> 18:02.440
and smile through the hardships

18:02.820 --> 18:04.600
just to survive.

18:05.380 --> 18:06.800
But you can be yourself

18:07.660 --> 18:09.680
when you're with me.

18:11.340 --> 18:13.440
I will respect
whatever decision you make

18:14.900 --> 18:16.200
and protect you.

18:17.580 --> 18:18.760
But

18:20.100 --> 18:22.760
I may not be a good wife.

18:24.060 --> 18:26.120
I can't submit to being just a wife

18:26.860 --> 18:28.440
who follows her husband's lead.

18:29.580 --> 18:32.440
But I will try to be your good partner.

18:37.660 --> 18:38.800
All right.

18:39.860 --> 18:41.000
All right, then.

18:41.420 --> 18:42.619
I won't

18:42.620 --> 18:43.800
let those rules bind you.

18:44.160 --> 18:45.590
You fear the seven rules of marriage.

18:46.500 --> 18:47.840
I'll make you seven promises.

19:09.700 --> 19:10.840
Your Lordship,

19:11.280 --> 19:12.840
the warehouse is filled with fireworks.

19:12.900 --> 19:14.880
We might not be able
to put out this fire.

19:17.180 --> 19:18.600
Then clear the surrounding area.

19:19.100 --> 19:20.099
Your Lordship.

19:20.100 --> 19:21.240
Don't let the fire spread.

19:21.250 --> 19:23.320
- Your Lordship, we'll clear it.
- Your Lordship.

19:23.400 --> 19:24.939
- How can you be so tactless?
- What's wrong?

19:24.940 --> 19:26.080
Just go.

19:26.380 --> 19:27.680
Su Xin. Su Lan.

19:29.020 --> 19:30.600
You should go and help too.

19:32.800 --> 19:34.379
It's your fault that we were discovered.

19:34.380 --> 19:36.840
I just want to see more clearly.

19:41.140 --> 19:43.600
Although I've agreed to this marriage,

19:43.780 --> 19:46.600
I fear it won't be easy

19:46.660 --> 19:48.200
for my Fifth Uncle, my father,

19:48.260 --> 19:50.499
or even your father to accept.

19:50.500 --> 19:51.760
It doesn't matter.

19:52.380 --> 19:54.379
Once I've decided to marry you,

19:54.380 --> 19:55.379
I'll take care

19:55.380 --> 19:57.080
of your father's side.

19:57.860 --> 20:00.840
It will be a proper marriage.

20:00.980 --> 20:02.680
How could I let you face it alone?

20:02.980 --> 20:04.240
I'll help you too.

20:12.620 --> 20:15.900
♪Riding across the desolate battlefield
in the wind♪

20:16.390 --> 20:19.480
♪The turbulence unfolding
one after another♪

20:20.640 --> 20:23.370
♪The lingering uncertainty
has yet been resolved♪

20:24.900 --> 20:27.299
It's just that the time we agreed on

20:27.300 --> 20:28.600
is approaching..

20:29.300 --> 20:31.080
I'm afraid there won't be enough time

20:31.220 --> 20:33.760
to hang the red silk on the tree.

20:33.980 --> 20:36.110
♪The expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

20:37.140 --> 20:38.320
It doesn't matter anymore.

20:40.200 --> 20:43.149
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

20:43.150 --> 20:45.279
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

20:45.280 --> 20:47.059
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

20:47.060 --> 20:47.999
It's so pretty.

20:48.000 --> 20:51.410
♪Your presence
my side is irreplaceable♪

20:51.610 --> 20:55.109
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

20:55.110 --> 20:58.990
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

21:11.900 --> 21:14.259
It seems like too much
to have the top hunter

21:14.260 --> 21:16.200
personally teach me how to ride.

21:16.300 --> 21:18.520
This horse is quite valuable.

21:18.540 --> 21:20.160
Are you really willing
to let me ride it?

21:20.260 --> 21:21.400
Of course.

21:21.460 --> 21:23.080
Do you like it, Your Highness?

21:23.940 --> 21:25.080
Of course.

21:25.540 --> 21:26.920
As long as you like it,

21:27.020 --> 21:28.440
I'd be happy to oblige.

21:28.760 --> 21:31.019
This is actually my first time riding.

21:31.020 --> 21:32.600
I'm a little nervous.

21:32.940 --> 21:34.720
The key to riding is relaxation.

21:35.740 --> 21:38.160
As long as you sit properly,
nothing will happen.

21:38.380 --> 21:39.520
Yantang,

21:39.540 --> 21:41.659
horseback riding is really fun.

21:41.660 --> 21:44.259
Could you come and teach me every day?

21:44.260 --> 21:45.560
If you're willing,

21:46.780 --> 21:47.960
it would be my pleasure.

22:14.300 --> 22:15.640
Stop playing.

22:16.300 --> 22:19.840
The melody of "The Mountain Spirit"
conveys deep and tender emotions,

22:20.100 --> 22:22.440
where the grace and charm
of the admired one shine through.

22:22.580 --> 22:25.280
You haven't yet grasped
the deeper meaning behind it.

22:29.340 --> 22:32.440
Now that Mother is gone,

22:33.380 --> 22:35.120
what's the point
of practicing these things?

22:35.820 --> 22:36.960
You...

22:38.140 --> 22:39.960
Your Grace. Second Young Master.

22:40.860 --> 22:42.000
What is it?

22:47.740 --> 22:51.040
Take some time to appreciate
this melody thoroughly.

22:51.060 --> 22:52.200
Yes, Father.

23:10.660 --> 23:11.539
Go on.

23:11.540 --> 23:15.419
His Lordship has been out with Princess Jingyu
for three days straight.

23:15.420 --> 23:17.419
They just went
to the racetrack together.

23:17.420 --> 23:19.120
Everyone is saying

23:19.140 --> 23:23.440
that they might've fallen for each other.

23:24.460 --> 23:28.280
His Majesty did have the intention
to grant the marriage during the hunt.

23:30.060 --> 23:32.840
He certainly didn't miss
this opportunity.

23:33.060 --> 23:35.240
Ever since Song Mo divided
the household,

23:35.340 --> 23:38.120
he has been acting recklessly
because of His Majesty's favor.

23:38.620 --> 23:41.160
If he becomes prince consort,

23:43.340 --> 23:45.680
he'll trample
the Duke of Ying's household

23:46.060 --> 23:47.880
under his feet.

23:48.940 --> 23:51.600
Marriage is dictated by the parents.

23:51.660 --> 23:55.520
If you set up a match
for His Lordship first,

23:56.020 --> 23:59.800
His Majesty won't be able
to grant a marriage, right?

24:03.180 --> 24:04.219
Your Grace,

24:04.220 --> 24:06.499
these are all young ladies
from prominent families.

24:06.500 --> 24:09.339
They are graceful and wise,
with gentle and virtuous personalities,

24:09.340 --> 24:12.400
all of a similar age to His Lordship.

24:19.820 --> 24:20.960
Leave.

24:25.260 --> 24:27.699
Your Grace, you seem dissatisfied.

24:27.700 --> 24:29.960
If you have any preferences,
feel free to say it.

24:34.620 --> 24:37.360
My son has a difficult temperament,

24:37.580 --> 24:40.200
no proper lady can tame him.

24:40.820 --> 24:42.680
You should find him

24:42.940 --> 24:46.000
someone strong-willed and sharp-tongued.

24:46.300 --> 24:47.600
A strong-willed woman?

24:50.540 --> 24:53.539
You certainly have a unique taste
in selecting a daughter-in-law.

24:53.540 --> 24:56.000
This is the first time
I've heard of such a thing.

24:57.660 --> 25:00.099
But there is one candidate.

25:00.100 --> 25:03.739
In the western part of the capital, the Fourth
Young Lady of the Dou Family, Dou Zhao.

25:03.740 --> 25:06.219
She's talented, proud,

25:06.220 --> 25:08.019
unreasonable, and fierce.

25:08.020 --> 25:11.419
She grew up in the countryside
in Zhending.

25:11.420 --> 25:13.680
They say she's quite
a strong-willed woman.

25:15.260 --> 25:16.619
Is that true?

25:16.620 --> 25:17.760
Absolutely.

25:17.780 --> 25:19.899
The Duke of Jining was willing
to bear the disgrace

25:19.900 --> 25:21.270
of leaving her to marry her sister,

25:21.280 --> 25:23.439
Fifth Young Lady Dou.

25:23.440 --> 25:25.179
That shows the Fourth Young Lady Dou

25:25.180 --> 25:27.379
is certainly not a gentle,
virtuous type of woman.

25:27.380 --> 25:28.580
Perfect.

25:29.420 --> 25:30.560
That's perfect!

25:32.180 --> 25:34.240
Get going and handle it.

25:34.300 --> 25:35.440
Yes, Your Grace.

25:42.460 --> 25:43.600
Your Grace,

25:43.860 --> 25:46.240
are you certain of Dou Zhao?

25:46.420 --> 25:48.080
What's wrong with the Dou Family?

25:48.460 --> 25:50.459
Song Mo and the Fifth Master Dou

25:50.460 --> 25:52.200
have been fighting like cats and dogs.

25:52.820 --> 25:55.320
If these two were to marry,

25:55.480 --> 25:57.040
there would be no peace

25:57.820 --> 26:00.200
at Yizhi Hall.

26:00.780 --> 26:01.920
By the way,

26:02.580 --> 26:04.000
to be safe,

26:04.340 --> 26:05.899
go to Zhending

26:05.900 --> 26:07.680
to gather information about this woman.

26:08.410 --> 26:09.259
Yes, Your Grace.

26:09.260 --> 26:11.960
(Tea)

26:12.500 --> 26:15.640
Fourth Young Lady's mother left her

26:15.820 --> 26:18.139
with maybe

26:18.140 --> 26:21.320
one or two thousand taels
of silver at most.

26:21.780 --> 26:24.339
The Fifth Young Lady's
maternal grandfather

26:24.340 --> 26:26.240
is the Minister of War.

26:27.180 --> 26:30.200
So she's definitely better off
than Fourth Young Lady.

26:31.180 --> 26:34.840
Isn't Dou Zhao the richest in Zhending?

26:35.460 --> 26:36.760
That was in the past.

26:36.820 --> 26:38.459
The maritime trade isn't doing well now.

26:38.460 --> 26:40.139
- Her wealth has almost been depleted.
- Exactly.

26:40.140 --> 26:42.819
Her family fortune is all managed
by the Madam of the Dou Family.

26:42.820 --> 26:44.179
Now, she's relying completely

26:44.180 --> 26:46.019
on her mother's dowry to get by.

26:46.020 --> 26:48.840
She's nothing but a sharp-tongued,
domineering woman.

26:49.220 --> 26:51.979
There was a heavy rain
that almost flooded Zhending.

26:51.980 --> 26:54.850
Originally, the idea was
to use sorghum instead of wheat.

26:54.860 --> 26:56.670
No matter how much we tried
to persuade her,

26:56.680 --> 26:58.320
Fourth Young Lady just wouldn't agree.

26:58.500 --> 27:01.499
She insisted on delivering the wheat.

27:01.500 --> 27:02.779
Isn't that forcing us?

27:02.780 --> 27:04.080
Not a strong-willed woman.

27:04.100 --> 27:05.699
But a poisonous one, a wicked one.

27:05.700 --> 27:07.090
Fourth Young Lady once set her eyes

27:07.100 --> 27:10.099
on Young Master Pang Kunbai
of the Pang Family

27:10.100 --> 27:11.640
and insisted on marrying him.

27:11.900 --> 27:13.819
Naturally, he refused.

27:13.820 --> 27:15.139
So she ordered her guards

27:15.140 --> 27:17.059
to beat him up.

27:17.060 --> 27:18.779
Dou Zhao is well-known
within a hundred li.

27:18.780 --> 27:19.939
Her grandmother raised her.

27:19.940 --> 27:21.950
But she's nothing more
than an ungrateful creature.

27:21.960 --> 27:23.170
In pursuit of a better family,

27:23.180 --> 27:25.450
she abandoned her grandmother
and returned to the Capital.

27:25.460 --> 27:27.110
She even bribed the county office,

27:27.120 --> 27:29.010
waiting for the Pang Family
to file a complaint.

27:29.020 --> 27:30.939
Young Master Pang was instead branded

27:30.940 --> 27:32.920
with a bad reputation
for bullying women.

27:33.460 --> 27:34.800
What a sin.

27:35.320 --> 27:37.260
Is she really that outrageous?

27:38.140 --> 27:39.879
It looks like she truly

27:39.880 --> 27:41.959
is a heartless and ruthless woman.

27:41.960 --> 27:43.099
(Yizhi Hall)

27:43.100 --> 27:45.019
I heard you

27:45.020 --> 27:47.200
spoke well of me
in front of His Majesty.

27:47.460 --> 27:50.059
Not only has His Majesty
reinstated my position,

27:50.060 --> 27:51.600
but he also praised me.

27:51.690 --> 27:53.289
The reason you were reinstated

27:53.290 --> 27:56.179
is because you have great foresight.

27:56.180 --> 27:59.229
His Majesty saw and approved
of your deep love for your daughter.

27:59.230 --> 28:02.080
Despite some criticism,
he couldn't bear to be too harsh on you.

28:02.720 --> 28:05.600
But I didn't do anything.

28:06.170 --> 28:07.139
That's not true.

28:07.140 --> 28:08.320
Not only for Dou Zhao,

28:08.400 --> 28:10.019
but we also have to thank you

28:10.020 --> 28:11.900
for the firecracker incident
in the suburbs.

28:12.060 --> 28:13.200
The firecracker incident?

28:13.740 --> 28:15.300
What does that have to do with me?

28:15.310 --> 28:16.910
You were not afraid of powerful figures

28:16.920 --> 28:18.819
and dared to beat Hai Changbo
out of the residence.

28:18.820 --> 28:21.440
Very few in the court have such courage.

28:21.700 --> 28:22.899
It's because of you

28:22.900 --> 28:24.720
that Hai Changbo was exposed,

28:24.860 --> 28:28.040
which led to the firecracker case
being solved so quickly.

28:28.060 --> 28:30.720
This accomplishment
belongs entirely to you.

28:31.180 --> 28:34.960
In truth, I should thank you.

28:36.300 --> 28:38.019
Hearing you speak this way

28:38.020 --> 28:39.240
is quite refreshing.

28:39.540 --> 28:41.120
- Please, have a drink.
- You too.

28:46.580 --> 28:47.840
This wine is excellent.

28:53.500 --> 28:55.960
It would be a waste to keep this wine
in my residence.

28:56.180 --> 28:57.360
Please accept them.

28:58.340 --> 29:00.400
This is an imperial gift,
Sweet Dew wine.

29:01.140 --> 29:02.760
As a token of my gratitude.

29:04.580 --> 29:07.480
The works of the hundred schools
of thought are vast and diverse.

29:08.180 --> 29:10.240
Yet, you can focus and study them.

29:10.340 --> 29:11.880
That's rare indeed.

29:15.220 --> 29:17.280
(The Spring and Autumn Annals)

29:19.500 --> 29:21.680
This is a rare edition
from the previous dynasty.

29:22.100 --> 29:23.419
If you like it,

29:23.420 --> 29:25.160
I'll give it to you.

29:25.660 --> 29:26.800
No, I can't accept this.

29:27.060 --> 29:29.080
A gentleman does not take
what others hold dear.

29:29.300 --> 29:30.459
Since you read it often,

29:30.460 --> 29:31.720
you should keep it.

29:34.300 --> 29:36.880
I've long heard that your handwriting
is graceful and elegant.

29:37.050 --> 29:38.620
But I've never had the chance to see it.

29:39.420 --> 29:42.480
These Four Treasures of the Study
deserve someone refined.

29:42.740 --> 29:44.320
It would be a waste

29:44.380 --> 29:45.560
for a military man like me.

29:49.240 --> 29:51.240
These are decorative ink sticks,

29:52.780 --> 29:54.800
a purple brush,

30:00.100 --> 30:01.480
and an enamel inkstone.

30:02.700 --> 30:05.960
It's said the inkstone can warm
the ink and keep it from drying.

30:09.460 --> 30:10.720
Absolute nonsense!

30:11.140 --> 30:12.959
Go out and ask around

30:12.960 --> 30:14.059
about how Song Mo seized

30:14.060 --> 30:15.800
his family's residence through coercion.

30:16.040 --> 30:17.940
After he saved me
when the horse was startled,

30:18.120 --> 30:20.920
I saw he wasn't as people say.

30:20.930 --> 30:22.909
He's talented
both in martial and literary skills,

30:22.910 --> 30:24.600
well-mannered and steady.

30:25.460 --> 30:27.520
People only envy the capable.

30:27.990 --> 30:30.319
I think the rumors outside are baseless.

30:30.320 --> 30:31.690
It's completely unfounded.

30:33.220 --> 30:35.660
I promised Ms. Longevity
she could decide on her own marriage

30:35.740 --> 30:37.720
after the bride replacement incident.

30:38.630 --> 30:40.320
Besides,

30:40.660 --> 30:42.250
she has an imperial decree.

30:42.900 --> 30:44.880
The world has truly turned upside down.

30:45.300 --> 30:47.560
She actually gets
to choose her own husband!

30:48.890 --> 30:51.000
Dou Zhao is being reckless.

30:51.970 --> 30:53.360
But you're being just as foolish.

30:55.950 --> 30:57.440
Even if you act foolishly,

30:58.140 --> 31:00.000
the Duke of Ying, that old fox

31:00.540 --> 31:02.200
surely won't agree to this marriage.

31:03.900 --> 31:05.040
Master!

31:05.220 --> 31:06.360
Master!

31:09.220 --> 31:12.059
Master, Duke of Ying has sent betrothal gifts
on Lord Song's behalf.

31:12.060 --> 31:14.040
The chests are all lined up
at the front gate.

31:15.340 --> 31:18.000
Are you saying it's
from the Duke of Ying, Song Yichun?

31:18.100 --> 31:19.179
Yes, Fifth Master.

31:19.180 --> 31:21.400
The visiting card clearly bears
His Grace's name.

31:28.770 --> 31:30.099
I was right, wasn't I?

31:30.100 --> 31:30.979
Within three days,

31:30.980 --> 31:33.039
your father will undoubtedly come
with a proposal.

31:33.040 --> 31:34.160
It's as you've predicted.

31:34.170 --> 31:35.819
If I openly express my wish
to marry you,

31:35.820 --> 31:37.219
he will make sure it doesn't happen.

31:37.220 --> 31:38.450
Instead, taking the opposite approach

31:38.460 --> 31:40.890
and letting him choose
a so-called beautiful yet unruly woman

31:40.920 --> 31:42.480
to ruin my match with the Princess.

31:42.700 --> 31:43.859
Of course,

31:43.860 --> 31:46.240
Princess Jingyu's support
has been crucial in all of this.

31:47.400 --> 31:49.590
Congratulations on your clever maneuver,
Your Lordship.

31:49.600 --> 31:52.200
Congratulations on a swift victory,
Fourth Young Lady.

31:56.140 --> 31:57.360
Mission accomplished!

31:57.380 --> 31:58.920
Success through hard work!

31:58.930 --> 31:59.979
A joyous and blessed union!

31:59.980 --> 32:01.259
United in purpose and action!

32:01.260 --> 32:02.880
Harmony in marriage,
with mutual support!

32:06.620 --> 32:08.499
Is that wrong?

32:08.500 --> 32:09.890
Or is it blessed with offspring,

32:09.900 --> 32:11.899
long-lasting prosperity,
success and prosperity,

32:11.900 --> 32:13.390
and fortune in the Year of the Dragon?

32:26.820 --> 32:27.960
Master,

32:31.460 --> 32:33.400
it's from the jeweler's shop.

32:38.740 --> 32:43.080
(For the long term,
this marriage is a great match.)

32:48.980 --> 32:50.400
Bring the betrothal gifts inside.

32:51.060 --> 32:52.200
Yes, Master.

33:06.050 --> 33:07.539
(Twilight in Spring)
A little higher.

33:07.540 --> 33:08.379
That's it.

33:08.380 --> 33:09.740
A little higher. A little bit more.

33:10.860 --> 33:13.219
(Twilight in Spring)

33:13.220 --> 33:14.059
Looks good.

33:14.060 --> 33:16.080
(Picturesque Scenery)

33:17.980 --> 33:19.480
The paper-cutting is stunning.

33:19.540 --> 33:20.379
It is, right?

33:20.380 --> 33:22.120
(Double Happiness)

33:23.620 --> 33:26.099
The sleeve length
should be shortened by half an inch,

33:26.100 --> 33:27.990
and the skirt could use
an extra inch in length.

33:35.180 --> 33:36.790
For the headdress,

33:36.800 --> 33:38.980
we can add a phoenix flying
through peonies embroidery,

33:38.990 --> 33:41.480
with some red and blue gemstones
and cat's eye gems.

33:42.850 --> 33:44.320
That's enough, Su.

33:44.900 --> 33:46.560
But stop fussing over these.

33:48.460 --> 33:50.160
You came all this way

33:50.380 --> 33:52.419
and we haven't even had
a moment to chat.

33:52.420 --> 33:54.539
You've been busy picking fabrics,

33:54.540 --> 33:56.899
measuring,
and choosing patterns non-stop.

33:56.900 --> 33:58.280
Look at your fingers.

33:58.380 --> 34:00.040
I'm enjoying it, though.

34:00.120 --> 34:01.760
Don't you dare say it looks bad.

34:01.770 --> 34:04.060
Even if you embroidered a bald phoenix,
I'd still wear it.

34:07.380 --> 34:09.310
By the way,
I've arranged an escort agency

34:09.320 --> 34:11.179
to deliver the private savings
you kept with me

34:11.180 --> 34:12.770
and the profits
from the potato business here.

34:12.780 --> 34:13.960
It is already on the way here.

34:14.020 --> 34:16.859
Are you sure Song Mo can be trusted

34:16.860 --> 34:18.560
with that much money?

34:19.060 --> 34:20.299
Ms. Longevity! Su!

34:20.300 --> 34:21.819
This is the 28th flower I tried

34:21.820 --> 34:22.939
for wedding pastries.

34:22.940 --> 34:24.980
Su Xin, Su Lan.
Try them on Ms. Longevity's behalf.

34:25.180 --> 34:27.080
I have an upset stomach.

34:27.220 --> 34:28.509
I have to go now.

34:28.510 --> 34:30.440
I need to help Su adjust
the wedding garment.

34:30.620 --> 34:31.760
You...

34:32.940 --> 34:33.939
Su.

34:33.940 --> 34:35.240
Ru,

34:35.380 --> 34:36.499
stop messing around.

34:36.500 --> 34:38.699
How can anyone digest

34:38.700 --> 34:41.200
seven to eight wedding pastries a day?

34:41.300 --> 34:42.459
But I just want to make

34:42.460 --> 34:44.240
the best pastries for Ms. Longevity.

34:44.380 --> 34:46.240
This is the best already.

34:48.780 --> 34:50.280
If you sent these out,

34:50.640 --> 34:52.360
half the snack shops in the Capital

34:52.380 --> 34:54.160
would have to shut down.

34:54.210 --> 34:55.350
Really?

34:55.420 --> 34:56.279
Did you hear that?

34:56.280 --> 34:57.420
Fourth Young Lady.

34:57.740 --> 34:58.779
- Fourth Young Lady.
- Grandmother.

34:58.780 --> 34:59.920
Grandmother.

35:00.100 --> 35:02.520
Old Madam won't
let anyone else touch this chest.

35:02.540 --> 35:04.720
She insisted on handing it
to you herself.

35:07.620 --> 35:09.960
I saved up

35:10.500 --> 35:12.400
these jewels and property for you.

35:12.890 --> 35:15.080
It never hurts to have a little extra
for your dowry.

35:15.700 --> 35:17.540
The more secure you are,

35:17.700 --> 35:19.560
the more at ease I'll be.

35:26.170 --> 35:29.640
This pendant is an heirloom
of the Cui Family.

35:30.020 --> 35:31.160
In the future,

35:31.260 --> 35:34.360
the elite officials
of the Cui Clan's Academy

35:34.660 --> 35:37.800
will support you
as His Lordship's wife.

35:41.100 --> 35:42.579
I even said

35:42.580 --> 35:44.360
I would take you out traveling.

35:44.820 --> 35:46.520
But I ended up marrying first.

35:48.540 --> 35:49.680
Grandmother,

35:49.820 --> 35:51.019
I'll definitely...

35:51.020 --> 35:52.160
No rush.

35:52.340 --> 35:54.640
Good things don't stick around
with troublemakers.

35:54.830 --> 35:57.210
As long as Song Mo values you,

35:57.920 --> 36:00.360
you'll find beauty
in every corner of the world.

36:00.570 --> 36:03.640
Marriage isn't the only path for women.

36:03.820 --> 36:05.129
Since you're getting married,

36:05.130 --> 36:07.840
make sure it's a marriage
that brings you happiness.

36:08.220 --> 36:09.840
If anyone mistreats you,

36:10.450 --> 36:12.000
don't suffer in silence.

36:12.120 --> 36:14.000
This will always be your home.

36:17.220 --> 36:19.059
By the way, we've been busy all day.

36:19.060 --> 36:20.840
Where's Uncle?

36:24.260 --> 36:27.019
This son of mine
might not be very good with words

36:27.020 --> 36:28.370
and a bit slow.

36:29.280 --> 36:32.750
At least he values loyalty
and keeps his promises.

36:33.220 --> 36:34.360
Ms. Longevity,

36:34.700 --> 36:38.480
the bracelet your mother left you
wasn't just one,

36:40.020 --> 36:41.320
it was a pair.

36:42.290 --> 36:43.430
A pair?

36:46.820 --> 36:49.920
Shiying was supposed
to wear the other one.

36:49.980 --> 36:52.219
When you were born, it was agreed

36:52.220 --> 36:53.899
that these bracelets would be passed on

36:53.900 --> 36:56.120
to you and your husband.

36:58.420 --> 37:01.000
(Two perfect jades, a perfect couple.)

37:01.540 --> 37:04.360
(Their love is pure and true,
like flawless jade.)

37:05.260 --> 37:07.600
(On the first anniversary
of Guqiu's death,)

37:08.020 --> 37:09.960
(Shiying buried both the bracelet)

37:09.980 --> 37:11.560
(and a jar of wine)

37:12.060 --> 37:14.520
(under the big tree in the manor.)

37:15.300 --> 37:16.920
(Years later,)

37:17.060 --> 37:20.440
(the tree was cut down
during the military settlements.)

37:20.700 --> 37:23.320
(Then several floods...)

37:23.500 --> 37:24.800
Ms. Longevity is getting married.

37:25.180 --> 37:26.320
Without this bracelet,

37:27.100 --> 37:28.720
how could Guqiu be at peace?

37:37.220 --> 37:38.360
Father.

37:51.420 --> 37:52.560
Forgive me,

37:53.420 --> 37:54.560
Ms. Longevity.

37:56.220 --> 37:57.520
Let us find it.

38:10.380 --> 38:12.120
Why are you standing here watching

38:12.580 --> 38:14.389
from a distance instead of going over?

38:14.390 --> 38:16.880
They said meeting before the ceremony
brings bad luck.

38:27.140 --> 38:29.280
It's just a bracelet,
is it worth all this?

38:32.540 --> 38:34.640
That bracelet holds memories
my mother left me.

38:34.700 --> 38:37.320
An emotionally detached person like you
wouldn't understand.

38:39.340 --> 38:41.080
You're feeling uncertain
about the marriage.

38:41.090 --> 38:42.830
So you're clinging
to something sentimental.

38:42.840 --> 38:44.920
Why don't I give you
something practical instead?

38:46.730 --> 38:48.379
This is a rare, fast,
and enduring horse,

38:48.380 --> 38:50.240
which I handpicked
from the Liaodong market.

38:50.250 --> 38:53.040
If you grow tired, start to regret,

38:53.140 --> 38:54.859
or be mistreated someday,

38:54.860 --> 38:56.419
you can ride it to find me at any time.

38:56.420 --> 38:58.210
I guarantee
Song Mo won't catch up with you.

38:59.220 --> 39:00.880
It's that Ji Yong again.

39:08.260 --> 39:09.400
Bai.

39:09.680 --> 39:10.820
Bai.

39:11.100 --> 39:12.240
Bai, come back.

39:14.180 --> 39:15.960
My mother spent her life hoping

39:16.340 --> 39:19.160
to be a perfect couple
with a strong mutual connection.

39:20.580 --> 39:22.960
But I still can't find
the other bracelet.

39:23.660 --> 39:25.480
Does this mean she's disappointed in me?

39:26.820 --> 39:27.960
Ms. Longevity.

39:43.420 --> 39:45.000
Why are you covering my eyes?

39:45.180 --> 39:47.440
Your father said meeting the bride
before the ceremony

39:47.900 --> 39:49.080
brings bad luck.

39:50.140 --> 39:51.480
I'll help you find it.

39:52.380 --> 39:53.600
There's no need.

39:54.180 --> 39:56.280
We've searched for so long.

39:56.540 --> 39:57.960
It's probably lost for good.

39:59.660 --> 40:01.659
There's so much to do for the wedding.

40:01.660 --> 40:02.980
You should go and take care of it.

40:03.300 --> 40:04.520
Don't worry about this.

40:15.290 --> 40:16.880
Tomorrow is the big day.

40:16.900 --> 40:19.560
As for the bride's departure,
I'll check over with you again.

40:20.180 --> 40:22.880
The dowry includes 100 taels of gold,
500 taels of silver,

40:22.900 --> 40:24.480
and five trunks of embroidered gowns...

40:24.900 --> 40:26.379
Let me go. I wasn't eavesdropping.

40:26.380 --> 40:27.520
Let me go!

40:27.900 --> 40:29.440
- Move!
- Let me go!

40:29.860 --> 40:32.680
His Lordship is about to get married,
and he dares to eavesdrop.

40:32.820 --> 40:33.899
- You rude brat!
- Speak!

40:33.900 --> 40:35.200
Who sent you here?

40:35.860 --> 40:37.000
Uncle?

40:38.020 --> 40:39.280
- Ms. Longevity?
- Uncle?

40:39.420 --> 40:40.560
Let me go!

40:41.470 --> 40:43.019
I didn't know it was you, Official Zhao.

40:43.020 --> 40:44.160
Forgive me for offending you.

40:44.380 --> 40:47.120
After fighting
to get half a month's leave,

40:47.140 --> 40:49.270
I rushed all the way here
to offer my congratulations,

40:49.340 --> 40:51.160
only to be mistaken for a thief.

40:53.260 --> 40:55.120
Tell me, do I look like a thief?

40:55.820 --> 40:57.280
With this many armed guards,

40:57.660 --> 40:59.840
is this a wedding or a prison?

40:59.980 --> 41:01.099
Sir,

41:01.100 --> 41:01.979
His Lordship stationed

41:01.980 --> 41:05.419
the guards here to prevent any mishap
like the bride switch incident.

41:05.420 --> 41:07.659
Seeing your muddy shoes
and lingering by the wall, I...

41:07.660 --> 41:09.840
- Come inside now.
- That's why I got it wrong.

41:13.140 --> 41:14.880
You messed up again.

41:17.780 --> 41:20.280
(Cui's Residence)

41:20.300 --> 41:21.800
You saw that, right?

41:22.880 --> 41:25.829
Just by looking at Song Mo's men,

41:25.830 --> 41:28.880
you can tell he's naturally suspicious
and ruthless in his ways.

41:29.060 --> 41:31.320
Are you really going to marry

41:31.560 --> 41:33.240
a cruel and violent man like him?

41:33.510 --> 41:34.650
Uncle,

41:35.080 --> 41:36.899
people say I'm selfish,

41:36.900 --> 41:38.960
fierce, greedy,

41:39.220 --> 41:40.760
and have the face of a shrew.

41:40.940 --> 41:43.099
Outsiders are bound to be biased.

41:43.100 --> 41:44.560
So their opinions don't count.

41:45.140 --> 41:46.760
Song Mo isn't like that.

41:47.500 --> 41:50.680
When he was in Futing,
he dedicated himself to the people,

41:50.740 --> 41:52.460
leading his troops to eliminate pirates.

41:52.470 --> 41:54.939
He is completely sincere and devoted
to protecting the people.

41:54.940 --> 41:56.590
How could he be a cruel
and violent thug?

41:57.860 --> 42:00.059
Don't let your feelings cloud
your judgment

42:00.060 --> 42:02.160
or be fooled by his appearance.

42:02.380 --> 42:03.859
I've heard rumors

42:03.860 --> 42:05.099
that he killed all the guards

42:05.100 --> 42:07.989
in his residence for no reason.

42:07.990 --> 42:10.680
Do you really think someone like that
could be a good person?

42:11.340 --> 42:12.479
Don't you realize

42:12.480 --> 42:15.520
a Duke's household
is a den of tigers and wolves?

42:16.660 --> 42:18.999
A noble family is not the same
as an official household.

42:19.000 --> 42:20.619
Just look at the Duke himself.

42:20.620 --> 42:24.019
The Duke of Ying's family
isn't exactly a good one to marry into.

42:24.020 --> 42:26.160
I know you are concerned for my sake.

42:26.220 --> 42:27.179
But I believe

42:27.180 --> 42:29.480
he truly cares for me
and will protect me.

42:30.060 --> 42:31.440
I am willing to marry him.

42:38.200 --> 42:39.760
Since you've made your decision,

42:41.500 --> 42:43.080
I'll support you.

42:43.860 --> 42:45.400
Your mother once said,

42:45.960 --> 42:48.480
there's no right or wrong in choices.

42:48.890 --> 42:50.739
As long as it comes from the heart

42:50.740 --> 42:52.040
and with no regrets,

42:52.260 --> 42:53.840
she would definitely support you.

42:55.000 --> 42:58.160
She never regretted marrying
your father.

42:58.580 --> 43:00.480
If Guqiu's spirit knows

43:00.980 --> 43:03.320
you've found a worthy husband,

43:03.820 --> 43:05.560
she would be even happier than I am.

43:23.410 --> 43:25.179
(Wang Yingxue)
Did you deliver that letter?

43:25.180 --> 43:28.040
I want to see
how she marries into that family.

43:28.540 --> 43:29.960
She was replaced the last time.

43:30.100 --> 43:32.020
This time,
they're breaking off the engagement.

43:32.040 --> 43:33.180
Dou Zhao!

43:34.790 --> 43:37.869
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart♪

43:37.870 --> 43:40.859
♪The dizziness of longing♪

43:40.860 --> 43:44.579
♪Like the sun waiting
for the flying wild geese♪

43:44.580 --> 43:47.970
♪The sound of weapons chasing
the long whip♪

43:48.460 --> 43:54.540
♪Never tired after a hundred battles,
because of you♪

43:54.850 --> 43:56.759
♪Morning and night, we meet again♪

43:56.760 --> 43:58.319
♪Walking slowly towards the distance♪

43:58.320 --> 44:01.690
♪Like leaves tangled in the wind,
tightly intertwined♪

44:01.730 --> 44:03.829
♪Together with you, wing to wing♪

44:03.830 --> 44:08.559
♪Our shadows flying,
dwelling together year after year♪

44:08.560 --> 44:10.339
♪Morning and night, with clear skies♪

44:10.340 --> 44:12.520
♪Clear wind and bright moon,
we wait for them♪

44:12.720 --> 44:15.339
♪Waiting for the fog to disperse
and the clouds to clear♪

44:15.340 --> 44:17.179
♪Tears that fall,
half a lifetime of tears♪

44:17.180 --> 44:21.580
♪Melted by your kiss,
melted by your kiss♪

44:22.120 --> 44:24.309
♪In this life, I wish to be
like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

44:24.310 --> 44:26.280
♪The green shore is more beautiful
than the sky♪

44:26.460 --> 44:29.109
♪The splendor doesn't intoxicate
the eyes♪

44:29.110 --> 44:30.839
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

44:30.840 --> 44:33.350
♪The mountains are distant,
what do I have to envy?♪

44:33.351 --> 44:35.859
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

44:35.860 --> 44:38.069
♪In this life,
I wish to keep my promise to you♪

44:38.070 --> 44:40.249
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

44:40.250 --> 44:42.859
♪I will definitely fulfill the promise
without fail♪

44:42.860 --> 44:48.950
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

44:57.220 --> 44:59.369
♪In this life, I wish to be
like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

44:59.370 --> 45:01.500
♪The green shore is more beautiful
than the sky♪

45:01.530 --> 45:04.149
♪The splendor doesn't intoxicate
the eyes♪

45:04.150 --> 45:05.839
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

45:05.840 --> 45:08.365
♪The mountains are distant,
what do I have to envy?♪

45:08.366 --> 45:10.889
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

45:10.890 --> 45:12.969
♪In this life,
I wish to keep my promise to you♪

45:12.970 --> 45:15.180
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

45:15.210 --> 45:17.859
♪I will definitely fulfill the promise
without fail♪

45:17.860 --> 45:24.100
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

45:28.140 --> 45:29.089
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:29.090 --> 45:30.069
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:30.070 --> 45:31.360
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
